    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  subjects 18 to 65 years of age

          -  a &gt;2 year history of asthma

          -  FEV1 &gt; 80% for subjects currently using Advair®.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe asthma

          -  current smokers

          -  pregnant or breast-feeding women

          -  other chronic significant illnesses
      </textblock>
